      <div class="chat-window" id="chat-window">
        <div class="msg">
          <div class="msg-avatar">ðŸ¤–</div>
          <div class="msg-bubble">
            <strong>Namaste! ðŸ™</strong> I'm your ET Money Mentor â€” an AI financial advisor trained on Indian tax laws, investment products, and market data.<br/><br/>
            I can help you with SIP planning, tax saving, insurance, home loans, retirement planning, and more. What's on your financial mind today?
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="chat-input-row">
        <input class="chat-input" id="chat-in" placeholder="Ask me anything about your finances..." 
          onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter') sendChat()"/>
        <button class="chat-send" onclick="sendChat()">Send â†’</button>
